      • lensPosition

        @Cast(value="uint8_t")
public byte lensPosition()
        Lens/VCM position, range: 0..255. Used with autoFocusMode = OFF. With current IMX378 modules: - max 255: macro focus, at 8cm distance - infinite focus at about 120..130 (may vary from module to module) - lower values lead to out-of-focus (lens too close to the sensor array)
